reviewText:
I've seen willie perform about a dozen times and he is always amazing!! Im' gonna cop this DVD day 1 for sure...its about time he got is own special!!

Go WILLIE!!

This guy was great on the tv show Comedy. TV and he was very funny without any of the bad language he says in this video. I wish that Comedy. TV would start releasing there own dvd's because a lot of the comedians are very funny and they all keep it clean so even teens can watch!! However, this show should have been rated R but a Canada based company (who released this) has a weird rating system!! This video was fairly funny but only adults should watch it!
Awesome!!! I love it... we laughed so hard... we are happy with our purchase thx Amazon. .
If you don't mind the mouthful of vulgarity, this guy is hilarious!  He's the "tell-it-like-it-is" kind of comedian and it's hard to disagree with what he says.
Love this guy he is so so funny he speaks some Spanish very funny Spanish I would recommend 100% any day everyday.

I just do not understand the other reviews for this "comedian".  Simply put, this act is NOT funny.  I sat through the entire thing, and never once laughed outloud, or even giggled.  The material is unoriginal and clich. I found myself arriving at the punch lines FAR before he could get there. How do the reviewers find ANY of this funny?!  It is quite discouraging that someone like Willie Barcena becomes famous when there are far more talented and undiscovered individuals on the comedy circuit.
I caught a piece of Willie's special on Comedy Central and purchased the DVD. Willie's a funny man. My boyfriend and I really had some great laughs.
Excellent Show.  I buy a lot of comedy CDs and this is up there with Ron White.
